wiki.summary: Sean Garrett, along with Bloodshy & Avant, produced "Toy Soldier."  Garrett also produced at least six more unreleased songs, including the leaked "Kiss Me All Over and "Pull Out" and the unreleased "Red Carpet" and "Love." Of Garrett's collaboration with Spears, he notes, "I've got this one record I've been holding for 10 months that everyone has tried to buy, but I stayed with Britney on it. I guarantee it will shake up the world. It's uptempo, out of control ...

track.name: Toy Soldier
comments: Best track on the album, hands down!
